In the D.E.D ship, Phebus spoke to Havok.  "The message has 
been recieved, but no repply has come.  I also have sattelite 
images of a pod from a faction known as "The Alliance" heading 
towards him with an ETA of 45 mins.  What shall I do Lordship?"

Havok pondered, then looked to Spinister.  "We will greet him 
personally.  Spinister. prepare to leave.  Bring along Needlenose. 
We must get this bot, and I would like to visit the Alliance."
